==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Trothplight
<hw>Troth"plight`</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Betrothed; espoused;
affianced.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trothplight</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Trothplight
<hw>Troth"plight`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of betrothing, or
plighting faith; betrothing.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trothplighted</ent>⟦br⟧
